<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.1">
<l>māṇikkak kiṇkiṇi yārppa maruṅkiṉmē</l>
<l>lāṇippoṉ ṉāṟceyta vāypoṉ ṉuṭaimaṇi</l>
<l>pēṇip pavaḷavāy muttilaṅ kappaṇṭu</l>
<l>kāṇikoṇṭa kaikaḷāl cappāṇi karuṅkuḻaṟ kuṭṭaṉē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While [your] ruby anklets jingle, having adorned beads of gold</l>
<l>that were made with superior gold upon [your] waist,</l>
<l>so that the pearls of [your] coral mouth shine,</l>
<l>[clap] cappāṇi with the hands that long ago grasped the land [of Mahābali].</l>
<l>O child with black curls, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
